{"tid":1419620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五大訴求VS林奠扣帽","createTime":"2019-08-06T02:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T02:48:30.000Z","uid":3177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"33048035be2e9870028df43f1d30498c34d858c8","tid":1419620,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:04:55.000Z","msg":"1. 撤回送中惡法<br />\n2. 收回暴動定義<br />\n3. 撤銷社運者控罪<br />\n4. 追究黑警濫暴<br />\n5. 落實雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n我相信大家都知！前線和理非都知！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n問題係政府 依家做乜撚野 佢都入你數 入落挑戰國家主權數， 反觀國家文宣機器 每次都描撚準備 直指 港獨旗號 2014年是否同樣手法? 你諗下想帶緊咩方向？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自由表達訴求=遊行集會 vs 拋國旗落海/衝擊警方/佔領 /影響經濟民生</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">777:他們揚言要「搞革命」，要「光復香港」。這些行為已經遠遠超越原來的政治訴求，這些挑戰國家主權，危害「一國兩制」的違法行為會摧毀香港的穩定繁榮。</span></em><br />\n<br />\n最終要帶出既信息係咩？ 係唔係直接就話你港獨？？ 你想佢回應訴求 ， 但每次就係話你衝擊一國兩制乜7底線，林鄭唔敢講 港獨 二字 ， 但中央好明確，輿論機器準備曬，港獨點點點！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">要成功唔可以忽視統戰/被統戰 ，要兼顧輿論/民意<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">雙普選唔係就係一國兩制下 應該要行同可行既方案咩？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">有人話「中共報導 / 震怒，代表中共害怕」，其實係啱啱相反。中共媒體係絕對唔會報導任何關於黨領導嘅不利消息，大家諗吓貿易戰就知。<br />\n<br />\n相反，佢報得嘅話，就必定對佢有著數。大家千祈唔好誤會，佢哋無論係咪真係「震怒」都好，無著數嘅嘢佢哋絕對唔會做。</span><br />\n</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老解進場  你仲嗌唔嗌光復香港我唔知我無權管<br />\n但政府<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">破壞一國兩制</span></span>底線一定要講!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u-9Qo0QxATg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Du-9Qo0QxATg&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKWqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=926c2d4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u-9Qo0QxATg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1418607/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1418607/page/1</a><br />\n被內地國安打到下頷骨折的人 給香港人的一封信<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同樣！希望大家可以思考下一步應該如何應對呢方面嘅局勢！</span></span>"},{"pid":"46f9a5ab351c18c9b752ad7dab74d2cb04036359","tid":1419620,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:12:46.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"801620541bbc542ff22aedb00ce7649cb9a12929","tid":1419620,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:15:42.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4a697dff9864e3dc692786eeec5b0683d3f145c7","tid":1419620,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:16:03.000Z","msg":"要成功唔可以忽視統戰/被統戰 ，要兼顧輿論/民意"},{"pid":"aea8b25d0adccb3d47396bcbff2952750c150fec","tid":1419620,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:18:03.000Z","msg":"破壞一國兩制!"},{"pid":"1c33a2830499489ed462c7a36dab64e71d840d22","tid":1419620,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:19:41.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3cfaf7661deca24e8dfd34f4ccece8cb689ffa63","tid":1419620,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:20:47.000Z","msg":"PUSH~"},{"pid":"82ffe050177c9ebb27521c6f990592233287acd8","tid":1419620,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:24:10.000Z","msg":"PUSH~"},{"pid":"98cb04918a00e73d61ab211b0212daa0b671a0e4","tid":1419620,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:26:20.000Z","msg":"PUSH~"},{"pid":"e9e929cc9e5c0b963a6edf9bc8fbe99eb9207b43","tid":1419620,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:38:31.000Z","msg":"uppp"},{"pid":"8593867e54322ab78a0f17e4b991bdaae0171072","tid":1419620,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:48:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/n